# AI Provider Configuration - Choose one or both

# Option 1: Alibaba Cloud API Key (for Qwen models)
# Note: DashScope may not be available internationally
# Get from: https://dashscope.console.aliyun.com/apiKey (China mainland only)
ALIBABA_CLOUD_API_KEY=your_alibaba_cloud_api_key_here

# Option 2: Google Gemini API Key (works internationally)  
# Get from: https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# - If you're in China mainland, use ALIBABA_CLOUD_API_KEY
# - If you're international, get a GEMINI_API_KEY from Google AI Studio
# - You can configure both, and the system will try Alibaba first, then fallback to Gemini
# - The monitoring/metrics API keys (like the ones you have) will NOT work for AI models

# COMPREHENSIVE DASHSCOPE MODEL SUPPORT (13 Models):

# TEXT GENERATION MODELS:
# - qwen3-max: Most capable Qwen3 model with deep thinking enabled
# - qwen3.5-plus: Enhanced Qwen3.5 multimodal model  
# - qwen3.5-35b-a3b: Large parameter multimodal model (35B parameters)
# - qwen3.5-27b: Large parameter multimodal model (27B parameters)
# - qwen-flash: Fast and cost-effective text generation

# IMAGE GENERATION MODELS:
# - qwen-image-2.0-pro: Advanced image generation with multiple reference images
# - qwen-image-max: High-quality image generation with detailed prompts
# - wan2.6-t2i: Text to image generation with enhanced quality

# VIDEO GENERATION MODELS:
# - wan2.6-r2v-flash: Reference video to video generation (motion transfer)

# AUDIO/Voice MODELS:
# - qwen-voice-design: Custom voice creation and design
# - qwen3-asr-flash: Speech recognition with automatic language detection
# - qwen3-omni-flash-realtime: Real-time voice conversation with multimodal support
# - cosyvoice-v3-plus: High-quality text-to-speech synthesis

# INTEGRATION:
# All 13 models are integrated across:
# - Code Assistant (Anita)
# - Image Tools (image generation, editing, analysis)
# - Video Tools (video generation, processing)  
# - PDF Tools (document analysis, summarization)
# - Audio Tools (voice design, ASR, TTS)

# Important: Use DashScope API keys, NOT monitoring/metrics keys
# Monitoring keys (like Prometheus/Grafana) will not work for AI models